{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "| 3 | Added `parse_qwscan failed` message when a `+QWSCAN:` line passes the prefix filter but fails to parse | Catches remaining format edge cases |", "ts": "2026-05-16T19:49:27+00:00", "time": "22:49:27"}
